name: (D)unkin parody shirt - limited/leftover qty.
description: Printed as an extremely limited edition "parody" tee, for a one-time only mail order special.  A handful were never followed-thru with by those who placed an advanced "size request" order, hence these few leftovers have been added to our band store.  Women's fitted tees are out. These are Men's cut, 4-color print on black tee.
